			<h2>We believe that...</h2>
			<ul>
				<li>Our data and our experience are equally important for understanding and engaging with our own health</li>
				<li>Experiential and emotional engagement with life-supporting and life-giving devices is critical to their potential</li>
				<li>Thinking with technology and experience equally will lead us to powerful health products and systems</li>
			</ul>
		</div>
