	<div class='column col6 edge'>
		<p>Through clever technology, empathic and intimate relationships and fluid interactions we design and build to create deeper connections. We come to the work through personal experience living with type 1 diabetes. We believe in making products and services that help us make meaningful relationships with our selves, our communities and our health care providers.</p><p> We want to know more and engage more. Our understanding of products and services that really work for patients is beautifully complemented with professional expertise in design, people centered research and software development.

		The potential of technology is fabulous but we don't want to get caught in the future. We want to make the potential now, and make it with and for people whose health can benefit from it - ourselves and you.</p>
